# Rejlers RAG V2 - Walkthrough

This file gives a quick walkthrough of how the app works end-to-end.

## 1) High-level purpose

The project is a Streamlit-based RAG system that:
- indexes project documents (PDFs + scraped StoryMaps sections),
- retrieves relevant chunks for a user query,
- generates an answer in Swedish (expert/citizen mode),
- shows sources and evaluation metrics.

